    "description": "We at KPIT Technologies Digital Technologies are looking for an experienced Full Stack Developer based out of Bhubaneswar. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout KPIT Technologies Digital Technologies:\nKPIT Technologies Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Python\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with KPIT Technologies Digital Technologies!",
